data.description: Homes like this don't come up very often. The home offers 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms and almost 2000 square feet of living space.  There are alSO picturesque views into the north Animas valley and west to Smelter and Hog's Back along with wide-spanning views over town make for a unique setting with great access. Located close to town, with HUGE views, functions large for the square footage. New appliances and air conditioning throughout. This classic in town Durango home sits on the north edge of the Ft. Lewis College mesa, overlooking the Red Cliffs of the Hermosa Valley with the tall alpine mountains as a backdrop...STUNNING! The house is perched on a rim lot adjacent North College Drive, which allows for quick and convenient access to town. The interior is spacious, sun-filled, and highly functional. With so many bedrooms (4) ...extra rooms can serve as guest rooms, a home office, a media room, a crafts room, a meditation room, a workout room, etc. The back yard is completely private, with lush green trees and privacy from the neighbors. Between the garage, basement and outdoor shed there is plenty of storage space for toys, holiday decorations, etc. Out the kitchen window is a walking path that accesses the Z-trail, Lion's Den, and Ft. Lewis College all popular destinations for locals! Don't miss this one.
